txt.en: The Ent sleeps once more. You have done all that you could at the White Hand encampment, and it is time to press further into the forest to assist more Ents.\n\nYou should try heading to the northern part of the forest and see what can be seen.
You have encountered a very distressed Huorn, trapped in a great tangle of sticky and cruel webs. He stands at the base of a stone stair, and you do not much like the feeling of this place.
You have done all that you can near the White Hand encampment; it is time to move deeper into Fangorn.
You discover a piteous Huorn, trapped in dense spider-webs
You should head to the northernmost parts of Fangorn to see what can be seen there.
You have encountered a very distressed Huorn, trapped in a great tangle of sticky and cruel webs. He stands at the base of a stone stair, and you do not much like the feeling of this place.
